text: Manyazybash () is a rural locality (a village) in Kukkuyanovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 30 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Dyurtyuli, 7 km from Kukkuyanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Manyazybash
